  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will test the effectiveness of face masks and hand cleaning in preventing the
      spread of influenza within households
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomised controlled trial of surgical masks and alcohol hand wash among approximately 6069
      Hong Kong residents who have a household member diagnosed with influenza. Influenza in index
      member and secondary infection will be documented with rapid influenza tests and PCR. Minimal
      risk to participants.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
